data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE 2/3 from 11-1pm*** Step into the welcoming all brick ranch with 1013 SqFt with  3 bedrooms, 1.1 baths, a finished basement, and a 2-car garage, all nestled on a generously sized lot. As you enter, bask in the abundant natural light gracing the spacious family room, revealing hardwoods beneath the carpeting. The kitchen features oak cabinets and all appliances are included  and a delightful eat-in area. Down the hall you have three sizable bedrooms and a spacious main bathroom. The finished basement, complete with an additional half bathroom, provides the perfect space for entertaining guests. Modern amenities include newer windows and a hot water tank, with 220 amps powering the entire house. Enjoy the covered back cement patio in the backyard – an ideal spot to relax. This home eagerly awaits your personal touch; come and explore the possibilities. Excluded from sale: Washer
